To offer quality media content to the Haitian public while respecting the rules ethics of the written press, radio and television;
- Help the Haitian citizen to better understand the underside of socio-political information that impact their daily lives;
- To participate in the construction of a Haitian citizen responsible to his country.

Our columnists, editors, writers, hosts and presenters strive to offer you the best in this global context marked by the reckless dissemination of fake news and unverified information on the internet.
Lakou Ayiti Media aims to be the voice of causes and actions aimed at the political and socio-economic development of Haiti.
